content.rendered:
Directed by Sampath Nandi.

Written by Sampath Nandi.

Cast Gopichand(Gautham / Nanda Kishore). Hansika Motwani(Heroine). Catherine Tresa(Heroine). Mukesh Rishi(Mudra). Chandramohan(Nanda’s father). Sachin Khedekar(Vishnu Prasad Ghattamaneni). Nikitin Dheer(Gowra). Ajay(Borabanda Bujji Yadav) . Annapoorna(Lakshmamma). Tanikella Bharani(Waiter). Pippa Hughes(News Reporter). Shree Radhe Khanduja(Nanda’s sister). Vennela Kishore(Kishore). Vidyullekha Raman(Spoorthi’s friend). Jayaprakash Reddy(JP Gowda). Niko Rusakov(Chef). Seetha(Nanda’s mother)

Language Telugu.

Producers Sahni Bob. Ravi Davande. Bhagawan J.. J. Pulla Rao.

Production Sri Balaji Cine Media. ZEE Entertainment Enterprises.
